content: I'm thinking of expanding my farm operations to include agritourism activities, like a farm stay program. I've been doing some research and planning, but I'd love some more information on what kind of licenses and permits I need to get started. Oh, and by the way, I finally finished building a new coop for my chickens today, and it's been a game-changer - they have so much more space now and I've noticed a significant increase in egg production.
